Older:

http://www.wonderworks.com/vm/
VM 7.19 is current as of December 31, 2005.
VM 7.18 is current as of July 1, 2004.  It was released November 2, 2003.
FAQ (http://www.wonderworks.com/vm/FAQ.html) was last revised Dec 8, 2003.
gnu.emacs.vm.info got 18 messages in June 2004.  Also see gnu.emacs.vm.bug
 http://groups.google.com/groups?hl=en&lr=&ie=UTF-8&group=gnu.emacs.vm.info
 http://groups.google.com/groups?hl=en&lr=&ie=UTF-8&group=gnu.emacs.vm.bug

